{"query": "was total visits less than 3 at any time since September 13? If so, please plot it as a line chart", "worker_responses": ["[analytics] Looking at the data from September 13 to November 29, 2023, I can see the daily total visits for each day. The **lowest** number of visits was **3**, which occurred on **October 1, 2023**. However, the condition was whether total visits were **less than 3** — meaning 2, 1, or 0. Since the minimum was exactly 3, no day had total visits below 3.

